{"id": 2211, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得哪些对男孩的教育必不可少？", "description": "倒是“你是个男孩子，所以你应该……”可以少一点。（题图来自：视觉中国）", "record_count": 5299, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201803061529076d17b5nP49iHeOoQ.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-03-08T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 269056, "content": "男孩子也得做家务活", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1268629}, {"id": 269057, "content": "你是个男孩子\n不要在女孩子面前像个狗一样\n懂得拒绝无理的要求\n自尊 自爱 \n单身不是耻辱\n不要让爱情变成痛苦\n承担应当的责任\n拒绝不存在的义务", "image": null, "praise_count": 215, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 964371}, {"id": 269058, "content": "敢作敢当", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1140685}, {"id": 269059, "content": "别太压抑自己，不然你会后悔三十年", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1279723}, {"id": 269060, "content": "别太压抑自己，不然你会后悔三十年", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1279723}, {"id": 269061, "content": "性知识的普及", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 669458}, {"id": 269063, "content": "爱和性别无关，别为了让自己看起来与众不同，做出让自己后悔的事请", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1280274}, {"id": 269064, "content": "说到就得做到，别轻易承诺", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1239102}, {"id": 269065, "content": "平等，爱，包容并且要做自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1270111}, {"id": 269066, "content": "性教育", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1104397}, {"id": 270346, "content": "少用手撸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1284648}, {"id": 269067, "content": "请少一点冲动 多了解下自己 偶尔压抑克制自己或许能改变将要发生的事儿 学会倾听", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1280296}, {"id": 269068, "content": "不要照着AV里的方式学习与女生发生关系。", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 75414}, {"id": 273165, "content": "长大后不要动手打自己的孩子。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1297980}, {"id": 269071, "content": "男孩子从小要学会尊重女性，保护女性，不能学老派的大男子主义，懂得且会收拾自己的仪容仪表，那种糙汉子系列的早就out 了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1269697}, {"id": 269072, "content": "如果给不了她未来 就别轻易地毁了她的现在", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1134750}, {"id": 269073, "content": "性教育", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 772780}, {"id": 269074, "content": "尊重女性！", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 260415}, {"id": 269076, "content": "勇气", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 597684}, {"id": 269078, "content": "明事理，懂规矩", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1279011}, {"id": 269079, "content": "做你想做的 温柔地对待他人对待自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1087734}, {"id": 269591, "content": "性教育", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1281221}, {"id": 269592, "content": "不要性骚扰强奸弱者，有这个想法的时候尽快就医。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 815297}, {"id": 269081, "content": "做个男子汉", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1280366}, {"id": 269082, "content": "小气 自以为是", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1136525}, {"id": 269594, "content": "尊重女性，认为自己的地位和女性是平等的，别总是仗着自己的生理优势（不会怀孕），就自认为天生高人一等。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1282555}, {"id": 269595, "content": "对感情专一不消耗感情，勇敢而不懦弱不软弱，不丧不佛系。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1282552}, {"id": 269084, "content": "多喝热水", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1280372}, {"id": 269085, "content": "挫折教育", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142839}, {"id": 269341, "content": "其实你可以温柔，也可以脆弱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1047384}, {"id": 269086, "content": "男性，作为社会的主导者，就要承担一些。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1278199}, {"id": 269342, "content": "一定要诚实，敢作敢当。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1281118}, {"id": 269087, "content": "化妆不代表“娘” 外表粗糙不代表“男子汉”", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1280383}, {"id": 269600, "content": "不管什么时候其他小朋友先动手时，别哑忍，别退缩，别犹豫，拳头挥回去！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 880347}, {"id": 269089, "content": "男孩纸也是爸爸妈妈的小宝贝，没必要事事让着女孩纸。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1280394}, {"id": 270625, "content": "礼貌教育，文明用语，责任感", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1285684}, {"id": 269090, "content": "心态大一些 不要太纠结于小事 ", "image": "img/option/option/20180308152022oHjlsaptFX0RKgnV.jpg", "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1280398}, {"id": 269091, "content": "责任", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1112469}, {"id": 269605, "content": "责任心，自己才是最强大的靠山，不要去求别人，要让别人来求你", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1282618}, {"id": 269094, "content": "不要只是上大号才擦，嘘嘘完也要擦一擦", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1280293}, {"id": 269606, "content": "诚实、正直、坚持并享受生活带给你的一切！漫漫人生路，不要试图去走捷径，那将辜负生活给你的期望！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1192171}, {"id": 270374, "content": "不同角色的为人处事", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1284735}, {"id": 269095, "content": "男人是可以倾诉的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 933228}, {"id": 269351, "content": "不要滥情，请尊重每一个喜欢你的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1269851}, {"id": 269096, "content": "自信，明辨是非！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1280414}, {"id": 269097, "content": "真心赞美女孩子", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1240811}, {"id": 269609, "content": "担当", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1019773}, {"id": 269098, "content": "男孩子也有权力追求好看哦，打扮的男孩不能称作“娘”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 977008}, {"id": 271658, "content": "树立规则感，又不能限制其发展，懂得两者均衡", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1291185}, {"id": 275242, "content": "在外受的冤屈，不应在家里进行暴力来发泄自己的愤怒?！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1311563}]}